dc_title_s: 1:1,000,000-Scale County Boundary Lines of the United States, 2014
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contains the county boundaries of the United States, Puerto Rico, and the U.S. Virgin Islands. This layer was derived from the 1:1,000,000-Scale County Boundaries of the United States polygon data layer. This layer is part of the 1997-2014 edition of the National Atlas of the United States.These data are intended for geographic display and analysis at the national level, and for large regional areas. The data should be displayed and analyzed at scales appropriate for 1:1,000,000-scale data. No responsibility is assumed by the National Atlas of the United States in the use of these data.
